These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, water, 7up, cola
4 different games are played: bridge, chess, backgammon, whist
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, d&b, rock, techno
 1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
 2. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 3. the fan rock is not to the right of the fan d&b##8
 4. the fan d&b is not to the left of the person playing whist##8
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is in an even position##4
 6. the person drinking water is on the right of the fan rock##1
 7. the person playing bridge is the fan country##1
 8. the fan rock is not the person playing whist##6
 9. the fan d&b is somewhere to the right of the person drinking 7up##5
10. the person drinking 7up is not to the right of the person playing backgammon##8
11. the person drinking water is not to the left of the person drinking 7up##8
12. the fan d&b is between the person drinking 7up and the person playing chess##2
13. the fan rock and the person playing backgammon have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |     3     |    4    |
| Hobby         | 7up | water      | cola | iced-tea |
| Job           | backgammon | whist | chess      | bridge |
| Music-Genre   | rock        | d&b            | techno    | country |

