.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, spy, fantasy, mystery
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, indie, jazz, r&b
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, may, january, october
 1. the fan jazz is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##8
 2. the person watching spy movies is not to the right of the person watching fantasy movies##8
 3. the person who's birthday is in may and the fan d&b have the same parity positions##9
 4. the fan jazz is somewhere to the right of the fan r&b##5
 5. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
 6. the person watching animation movies is not to the left of the person watching spy movies##8
 7. the fan r&b is not to the right of the person watching mystery movies##8
 8. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person watching spy movies and the person watching fantasy movies##2
 9. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the fan indie##1
10. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the fan r&b##1
11. the fan d&b is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##8
12. the fan r&b is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##8
13. the fan r&b is on the left of the fan jazz##1
14. the fan jazz is not to the left of the person watching mystery movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage      | spy | animation   | fantasy     | mystery     |
| Music-Genre   | indie    | d&b   | r&b      | jazz    |
| Sport         | october   | may | january | july |

