 3. the person watching spy movies is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 4. the person watching spy movies is somewhere between the person watching comedy movies and the person who likes ivory##7
 5. the person who's hobby is video-games and the person watching martial-arts movies have different parity positions##9
 6. the person who likes amber is not to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##8
 7. the person who likes amber is somewhere to the left of the person watching comedy movies##5
 8. the person who likes ivory is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##5
 9. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
10. the person who likes grey is between the person watching martial-arts movies and the person who likes yellow##2
11. the person who's hobby is fishing is not the person watching martial-arts movies##6

