The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, lacrosse, rowing, sailing
 1. the person who's birthday is in january and the person who growsbellflower have the same parity positions##9
 2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who growsmarigold have different parity positions##9
 3. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
 4. the person who growsmarigold is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##5
 5. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 6. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
 7. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 8. the person who growsiris is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdaffodil##5
10. the person who growsiris is between the person who's sport is rowing and the person who growsbellflower##2
11. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | november  | february        | january  | july |
| Hobby      | marigold  | iris    | bellflower | daffodil |
