.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, funk, ambient, d&b
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, ferret, lizard, rabbit
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, purple, ivory, orange
 1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
 2. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
 3. the person who likes purple is not the owner of the chinchilla##6
 4. the fan funk is on the right of the fan punk##1
 5. the fan funk is somewhere to the left of the person who likes purple##5
 6. the fan punk is somewhere to the left of the fan ambient##5
 7. the fan ambient and the person who likes purple have different parity positions##9
 8. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
 9. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
10. the fan punk is not to the right of the fan funk##8
11. the owner of the chinchilla is not the person who likes purple##6

